SolarHybrid Sees Full-Year Ebit of at Least $15 Million

-- B y   M a r i a j o s e   V e r a
-- 
2011-10-05T06:06:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-05/solarhybrid-sees-full-year-ebit-of-at-least-15-million.html
SolarHybrid AG (SHL)  raised its revenue
forecast to more than 400 million euros in the current fiscal
year with earnings before interest and tax of ‘at least’ 15
million euros.  The company received two contracts for the the construction
of large scale solar power plants Werneuchen and Allstedt I in
 Germany . Both power plants will be grid connected in 2011 along
with all other projects which are under construction.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mariajose Vera at 
 mvera1@bloomberg.net  